show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Flora’s heartbreak leads her to Vito Morelli — a vampire whose past is tied to her face. When love, revenge, and supernatural secrets collide, it sparks a romance that breaks hearts and takes lives. Watch Dracula’s Kiss, where one kiss changes everything.
